oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Mr. and Mrs. Melonger of Little Cove seated in front of a wooden building. He has a mustache and wears Blue Gem overalls with a collared shirt. She is in a dark patterned button up with white collar, and has a heart pinned to her blouse.
